title: Default values not displayed in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: When accessing the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values of the parameters are not being displayed.
OB: When accessing the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values of the parameters are not being displayed.
EB: When accessing the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values of the parameters should be displayed.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Create several report parameters and set default values for them.
2. Drag the parameters to the layout.
3. Access the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog and observe that the default values are not displayed.
